    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1883-06-05T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1883-06-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="407" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d407">
                <head>No. 406.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Frelinghuysen</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Morgan</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department
                                    of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1883-06-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">June</hi> 5,
                            1883</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>If agreeable to Mexican Government, will be glad to extend agreement of July
                        29 to term first fixed, or one year from August 18 next. You are authorized
                        to conclude agreement on either basis.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>FRELINGHUYSEN.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
